descriptionHtml:
Now you can play Baby Hazel Craft Time game app on your android mobile for free.

Festive holidays are over! Oh! But little princess has not yet complete her preschool craft assignment. Can you help her? Go creative and assist Baby Hazel in making unique crafts for her class assignment. Time is limited, be quick!

Baby Hazel enjoyed her school vacations by playing games and spending time with her pets. Oh no! But she forgot to complete her preschool craft assignment. Now she needs your help in completing her assignment. Go along with Hazel to buy essential supplies required for making crafts. Help her in making beautiful and unique craft within given time to get a surprise gift from her teacher. Enjoy craft time with Hazel!

• Go to stationary shop along with Baby Hazel to buy supplies required for crafting
• Assist her in making a flower pot using clay and color it
• One more craft to make…help Hazel in making colorful jelly fish
• Join Baby Hazel and her friends in class to enjoy some mischievous activities
• Let's see how much Hazel scores for her craft assignment
• Wish all the best to Hazel for glass painting the vase.
